{"tid":1660792,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇硬淨縮骨遮推介","createTime":"2019-10-17T17:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T09:30:47.000Z","uid":59221,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b6515241cb84530fc27fe620a2290367751f6c","tid":1660792,"uid":59221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:09:27.000Z","msg":"早幾個月買把u記無耐就爛左<br />\n想買把好少少 希望500樓下啦 除左梁蘇記仲有冇其他選擇<br />\n暫時睇岩blunt同euroschirm<br />\nblunt睇落幾好 不過聽聞好似幾細把下 同埋好似得logon有 食水有d深 但官網又斷哂貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\neuroschirm outdoor果把睇測試片好硬淨<br />\n但收納唔算太好同埋最重要係得藍店永高行有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實日本果把unnurella我都有睇過 但好似唔防風 同埋好細把<br />\n好難揀 有冇巴打有其他推介呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec2113c5922aeb6fb735eed290d5f62abdd543d","tid":1660792,"uid":199689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:13:09.000Z","msg":"縮骨遮唔硬淨得去邊<br />\n總有爛嘅一日<br />\n買把平嘅好過 話者買長遮"},{"pid":"21b43f8605246fed5ef17187f7b1e593ff1d114d","tid":1660792,"uid":137160,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QdLiU8Tt0f0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQdLiU8Tt0f0&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=71e35310\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QdLiU8Tt0f0</a>"},{"pid":"c8653f673e533c9d413cd8a7b67d2450a1d5b2df","tid":1660792,"uid":59221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec2113c5922aeb6fb735eed290d5f62abdd543d","tid":1660792,"uid":199689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:13:09.000Z","msg":"縮骨遮唔硬淨得去邊<br />\n總有爛嘅一日<br />\n買把平嘅好過 話者買長遮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"都係既 但防風同大把少少都有掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4b182305ed06e0931f966b561a5b0a44c6efc6","tid":1660792,"uid":59221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":